@startuml LobbySequence
actor HostPlayer
actor ClientPlayer
participant "Server (Host)" as Server
participant "Client (Joiner)" as Client

== Game Creation ==
HostPlayer -> Server : Host Game()
Server -> Server : ENetHost_create()
Server -> Server : Enter LobbyPhase
Server -> Server : LobbyPhase::onEnter()

== Joining ==
ClientPlayer -> Client : Join Game(IP)
Client -> Client : ENetHost_create()
Client -> Client : ENetHost_connect(IP)
Client -> Server : ENet Packet (Connect Request)

Server -> Server : OnConnect()
Server -> Server : Assign Peer ID
Server -> Client : Packet (Welcome + LobbyInfo)
Client -> Client : ScreenManager::setScreen(LobbyScreen)
Client -> Client : LobbyScreen::updateUI(LobbyInfo)

== Prepare Game (Loading) ==
HostPlayer -> Server : Start Game()
Server -> Server : Locked Lobby
Server -> Server : Load Level Data
Server -> Server : Transition to GamePhase
Server -> Server : Spawn Entities (Authoritative Registration)
Server -> Client : Packet (GameInit + MapID + Seed + InitialSnapshot)

Client -> Client : ScreenManager::setScreen(LoadingScreen)
Client -> Client : MapsManager::loadMap(MapID)
Client -> Client : Create Entities (GameScreen::onEnter)
Client -> Client : Apply InitialSnapshot
Client -> Server : Packet (ClientReady)

Server -> Server : Wait for all ClientReady

== Start Game (Go!) ==
Server -> Client : Packet (GameStart)
Client -> Client : ScreenManager::setScreen(GameScreen)
note right of Client : Start Game Loop Updates

== Gameplay ==
note right of Server : Both sides now run GameLoop Sequence
@enduml
